1. Get the native input element and modify its value

   *  use ref   
```
<input  :value='num' @change='handleChange' ref='inputnumber' />
...
handleChange(event){
   this.num=this.check(event.target.value);
   this.$refs.inputnumber.value=this.num;
}
``` 
   *  use event  

```
